": {"text": "当地时间 5 月 29 日，特斯拉和 SpaceX 公司的首席执行官马斯克在推特表示，「中国的航天计划比大多数人意识到的更加超前。」 29 日，首位执行太空漫步的加拿大航天员克里斯‧哈德菲尔德在推特发布帖子：「‘到 2030 年，中国人一定能够踏上月球。这不是问题，’月球探测计划的总设计师吴说。」，并附上了一张我国以月球为中心的深空互联网示意图。 据观察者网查证，此画面出自一条演示动画，4 月 24 日曾在央视新闻频道播出。 马斯克跟评并转发称：「中国的航天计划比大多数人意识到的更加超前。」 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-899d2f853e7366b5c9c530e6209597c3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603792670"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5fiCrYDpsccyEAMaCDk2NDU2NDYwINO41aMGMAw48wJAC3IJNjAzNzkyNjcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1685493938.6751099", "card_id": "Q_598499331", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 12}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为啥我总觉得复活后的大蛇丸不是真正的大蛇丸？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "纲手也说大蛇丸变了，会不会从咒印中复活的只是原版大蛇丸的情感意识分身，而且从红豆的咒印中复活的只是早期意志情感。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-3194302cd16eb90ef3558b22fdb97174_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/598499331"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I5fiCrYDpsccyEAMaCDk1MjgwMzM3IIbet6IGMAA4K0AMcgk1OTg0OTkzMzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1685493938.6758845", "card_id": "Q_602238086", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 125}